      Team-built autonomous robot for MIT’s MASLAB competition, integrating perception,
      state-machine autonomy, and manipulation under real-time constraints.
    </p>
    <div class="tags">
      <span class="tag">Autonomy</span>
      <span class="tag">Perception</span>
      <span class="tag">ROS2</span>
      <span class="tag">Systems</span>
    </div>
  </a>

